<section class="section" id="why">
    <div class="section__container">
        <div class="section__eyebrow">Why Tldraw.Blazor</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">Everything you need for infinite canvas</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Ported from the tldraw SDK to pure C# — a production-grade canvas engine for .NET developers.</p>
        <div class="why-grid">
            <div class="why-card">
                <div class="why-card__num">01</div>
                <h3 class="why-card__title">Canvas infrastructure</h3>
                <p class="why-card__desc">Viewport culling, shape caching with SKBitmap, adaptive grid rendering. Handles thousands of shapes without frame drops.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
                <div class="why-card__num">02</div>
                <h3 class="why-card__title">Accelerate development</h3>
                <p class="why-card__desc">8 shape types, 8 interactive tools, arrow bindings, undo/redo, clipboard, and touch support — all built in.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
                <div class="why-card__num">03</div>
                <h3 class="why-card__title">Customize, extend, control</h3>
                <p class="why-card__desc">Reactive store with change events. Shape utils for custom rendering. Style system with color, fill, stroke, opacity, dash, radius, and font controls.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
                <div class="why-card__num">04</div>
                <h3 class="why-card__title">Pure C# — no JS required</h3>
                <p class="why-card__desc">Core logic runs entirely in C# via SkiaSharp. Hardware-accelerated rendering with minimal JavaScript interop.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="section__container">
        <div class="section__eyebrow">Use cases</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">What you can build</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">From whiteboards to workflow tools — Tldraw.Blazor powers canvas-based apps of any kind.</p>
        <div class="showcase-grid">
            <div class="showcase-card">
                <div class="showcase-card__img"><div class="showcase-card__img-inner">whiteboard-preview</div></div>
                <div class="showcase-card__body">
                    <div class="showcase-card__tag">Whiteboard</div>
                    <h3 class="showcase-card__title">Collaborative Whiteboard</h3>
                    <p class="showcase-card__desc">Real-time drawing canvas with freehand strokes, shapes, text, arrows, and eraser tools. Multiplayer-ready with SignalR.</p>
                    <a href="docs/quick-start" class="showcase-card__link">Read more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="showcase-card">
                <div class="showcase-card__img"><div class="showcase-card__img-inner">flow-builder-preview</div></div>
                <div class="showcase-card__body">
                    <div class="showcase-card__tag">Flow Builder</div>
                    <h3 class="showcase-card__title">Visual Flow Editor</h3>
                    <p class="showcase-card__desc">Arrow bindings snap endpoints to shapes and auto-follow when nodes move. Build workflow editors, mind maps, and diagram tools.</p>
                    <a href="docs/arrows" class="showcase-card__link">Read more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="showcase-card">
                <div class="showcase-card__img"><div class="showcase-card__img-inner">design-tool-preview</div></div>
                <div class="showcase-card__body">
                    <div class="showcase-card__tag">Design Tool</div>
                    <h3 class="showcase-card__title">Design &amp; Prototyping</h3>
                    <p class="showcase-card__desc">8-handle resize, rotation, alignment, distribution, z-ordering, and grouping. A full selection and transform system.</p>
                    <a href="docs/selection" class="showcase-card__link">Read more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="showcase-card">
                <div class="showcase-card__img"><div class="showcase-card__img-inner">presentation-preview</div></div>
                <div class="showcase-card__body">
                    <div class="showcase-card__tag">Presentation</div>
                    <h3 class="showcase-card__title">Slide &amp; Canvas Apps</h3>
                    <p class="showcase-card__desc">Frame shapes with labels, image loading from file picker, export to PNG/SVG, and auto-save to localStorage every 5 seconds.</p>
                    <a href="docs/persistence" class="showcase-card__link">Read more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="inside">
    <div class="section__container">
        <div class="section__eyebrow">SDK Reference</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">What's inside</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">A complete SDK for building canvas-based applications in Blazor.</p>
        <div class="inside-grid">
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 3v18"/><path d="M3 9h6"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Selection &amp; Transform</h3>
                <p>Full selection logic with click, shift-click, rubber-band. Resize with 8 handles, rotation, multi-shape transform.</p>
                <a href="docs/selection" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Arrow System</h3>
                <p>Create arrows with auto-binding endpoints. Edit endpoints, rebind to shapes, visual feedback with green/blue dots.</p>
                <a href="docs/arrows" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Layout &amp; Composition</h3>
                <p>Alignment (6 directions), distribution, z-ordering, grouping/ungrouping. All via context menu or API.</p>
                <a href="docs/layout" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4M2 12h4m12 0h4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83m8.48 8.48 2.83 2.83M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83m8.48-8.48 2.83-2.83"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Style System</h3>
                <p>Style panel with color, fill, stroke, opacity, dash, radius, font controls. Customizable per shape.</p>
                <a href="docs/styling" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"/><polyline points="17 21 17 13 7 13 7 21"/><polyline points="7 3 7 8 15 8"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Persistence</h3>
                <p>Auto-save to localStorage every 5 seconds. Export/Import JSON, PNG, SVG. Image loading from file picker.</p>
                <a href="docs/persistence" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="inside-card">
                <div class="inside-card__icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Reactive Store</h3>
                <p>Centralized record store with change events. JSON polymorphic serialization. Snapshot-based undo/redo.</p>
                <a href="docs/store" class="inside-card__link">Learn more <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

